<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;">et Champagne Party au BOCAL dès 20:00 </span><a href="http://champagne.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83452e88669e20162fbed378e970d-pi" style="display: inline;"> </a><a href="http://champagne.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83452e88669e20154366b7003970c-pi"><img alt="Bocal" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d83452e88669e20154366b7003970c" src="http://champagne.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83452e88669e20154366b7003970c-800wi" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="Bocal" /><span style="font-size: small;"> </span></a><a href="http://www.terresetvinsdechampagne.com/" style="display: inline;" target="_blank"><img alt="TVC" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d83452e88669e20154366b7042970c" src="http://champagne.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83452e88669e20154366b7042970c-300wi" style="width: 280px;" title="TVC" /></a><br /><span style="font-size: small;"><br /></span><a href="http://champagne.typepad.com/.a/6a00d83452e88669e201539297d667970b-pi" style="display: inline;"><span style="font-size: small;"> </span></a><span style="font-size: small;">avec la fine Equipe <a href="http://www.terresetvinsdechampagne.com/" target="_blank">Terres et Vins de Champagne</a> en mode &quot;Champagne Coquillages &amp; Crustacés&quot; pour l&#39;occas.</span> •<span style="font-size: small;"> </span>Champagnes des Terres et Vins et Bring Your Own Bottle<span style="font-size: small;"> </span>• <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=27+rue+de+Mars+reims&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;hnear=27+Rue+de+Mars,+51100+Reims,+Marne,+Champagne-Ardenne,+France&amp;t=h&amp;z=16&amp;vpsrc=0" target="_blank">Bocal</a> • 27 rue de Mars • 51100 Reims, Champagne • FRANCE • phone: <a href="tel:%2B33%20%280%293%2026%2047%2002%2051" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ee6600;">+33 (0)3 26 47 02 51</span></a></p>
